dc_description_s: [This dataset includes boundaries for the Wisconsin Technical College System regions. This layer was created using unified and secondary public school district boundaries for the state of Wisconsin. Authoritative information used to create this dataset came from the Wisconsin Technical College board policy manualwhich was current as of December 2017 and last updated in November 2012.]
uw_supplemental_s: Archived dataset at UW-Madison. For more information and most current data please visit: https://data-wi-dpi.opendata.arcgis.com/
